#. Description of the theme
#: style.css
#, gp-priority: high
msgid "EazyShop is a fast, clean, lightweight theme. EazyShop is customizable and modern-looking free responsive WooCommerce WordPress theme for e-commerce stores like clothing, fashion, electronics, ebooks, dress store, sports shop, marketplace, multivendor, equipments or online products. Theme is compatible with Elementor, WPML, Polylang, Yoast SEO, WooCommerce, Contact Form 7, Jetpack and other popular plugins. The theme is SEO friendly, WPML and RTL ready. Looking for a WooCommerce theme? Look no further! EazyShop Pro demo https://demos.wpfable.com/premium/eazyshop/"
msgstr "EazyShop 是一个快速、干净、轻量级的主题。 EazyShop 是可定制且外观现代的免费响应式 WooCommerce WordPress 主题，适用于服装、时尚、电子产品、电子书、服饰店、体育商店、市场、多供应商、设备或在线产品等电子商务商店。主题与 Elementor、WPML、Polylang、Yoast SEO、WooCommerce、Contact Form 7、Jetpack 和其他流行插件兼容。主题适合 SEO，支持 WPML 和 RTL。正在寻找 WooCommerce 主题？别再犹豫了！ EazyShop Pro 演示 https://demos.wpfable.com/premium/eazyshop/"

